9 EFFECTIVE DATE
10 SECTION 3. Section 2 of this act becomes effective only if the constitutional
11 amendment proposed by Section 1 of this act is approved. If the constitutional amendment is
12 approved, Section 2 of this act becomes effective January 1, 2027. The remainder of this act is
13 effective when it becomes law.
